bert_Ehrenstein", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "118688227"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q214947", "wikipedia_page_title": "Albert Ehrenstein", "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": "E", "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/011770/2004-08-26"}